This project is part of the Enterprise Automation level Hybrid Automation Framework, which is based on:
Selenium with Python
Pytest Framework
Requests Library
Allure Reporting
Jenkins CI/CD
Selenium Grid
Docker
pytest is a tool for parallel testing: pytest-xdist.
Both are automated via the framework:
UI Testing
API Testing
Hybrid End-to-End Testing
Application Under Test:
UI: [https://practice.expandtesting.com/notes/app]
API: [https://practice.expandtesting.com/notes/api/api-docs/]
# Framework Features
# UI Automation
Selenium WebDriver
Page Object Model (POM)
Explicit Waits
JavaScript Executor
If it does not capture any screen shot.Not taking an image of the screen.
Reusable Components
Error Handling Utilities
# API Automation
Requests Library
Reusable API Client
Centralized Configuration Management
API Validation
Response Validation
Performance Validation
# Hybrid E2E Automation
# UI → API Validation
Create note via UI
To validate the same note in the API response.
# API → UI Validation
Delete an item from a note list with the API.
No more Jr. - Validate note in UI.
